@startuml
title Feature Journey Across Multiple Teams (Misaligned Boundaries)

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor DarkGray
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
}

participant "Team 1" as T1
participant "Team 2" as T2
participant "Team 3" as T3
participant "Shared Service Team" as Shared

== Small Feature Request ==

autonumber

actor User as U

U -> T1 : Request small feature
T1 -> T2 : Dependency / API change
T2 -> Shared : Needs shared module update
Shared -> T3 : Needs DB change / migration
T3 -> Shared : Adjust shared schema
Shared -> T2 : Update shared business logic
T2 -> T1 : Integrate and test
T1 -> U : Feature delivered\n(after many handoffs)

note over T1,T3
  Warning signs:
  • 3–5 teams for a small change
  • Many cross-team meetings
  • Fuzzy ownership of shared modules
end note
@enduml